## 4. NOTIFICATION TOOLS AND UTILITIES

The notification service provides several tools and utilities to facilitate integration, testing, and validation.

### 4.1 Tool Interface Overview

Internal system components interact with notification functionality through a standardized tool interface. This approach ensures consistent implementation and behavior across the platform.

#### 4.1.1 Tool Call Format

Internal tool calls follow a standardized JSON format:

```json
