| send_email | Send email notifications | To, Body | Subject, Format, Attachments |
| send_sms | Send SMS messages | To, Body | Priority |
| call_webhook | Invoke webhook endpoints | Url, Payload | Method, Headers |
| publish_event | Publish to event queues | Topic, Message | Attributes, Delay |

